:0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:42:24.000Z","msg":"如果佢又支持公投又唔比人投票就獨裁姐<br />\n事實上而家香港嘅情況下 公投真係好大獲嘛<br />\n所以佢咪唔支持囉"},{"pid":"ba38b1be4b569934d9a757082d6db5ae696ea8a8","tid":307014,"uid":10894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T11:44:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"54ebba18fb19147c8544b1e25f0251c2873336c7","tid":307014,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果佢又支持公投又唔比人投票就獨裁姐<br />\n事實上而家香港嘅情況下 公投真係好大獲嘛<br />\n所以佢咪唔支持囉</blockquote><br />\n咁佢就唔好up乜野 公投要篩選la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢無咁講，咪做標題黨"},{"pid":"c021e75182342d9ebb7df278148e92a1c7c843be","tid":307014,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"又有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哩點冇諗過[/quote]<br />\n除左原居民冇任何移民有佢所謂既legitimacy<br />\n因為香港由頭到尾冇真正實行過民主<br />\n請問游水落黎果班又有乜野legitimacy?[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n所以未來香港係需要界定何謂公民，否則所謂既「民主」係亳無意義既民主"},{"pid":"4d76422c725a2251afa5191695ec55fe1395078e","tid":307014,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"[/quote]<br />\n除左原居民冇任何移民有佢所謂既legitimacy<br />\n因為香港由頭到尾冇真正實行過民主<br />\n請問游水落黎果班又有乜野legitimacy?[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n所以未來香港係需要界定何謂公民，否則所謂既「民主」係亳無意義既民主[/quote]"},{"pid":"d17a270ce4ed171dbadbdf17df6c31e048d3d7cc","tid":307014,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:54:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又有道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n哩點冇諗過</blockquote><br />\n除左原居民冇任何移民有佢所謂既legitimacy<br />\n因為香港由頭到尾冇真正實行過民主<br />\n請問游水落黎果班又有乜野legitimacy?[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n所以未來香港係需要界定何謂公民，否則所謂既「民主」係亳無意義既民主[/quote]<br />\n你地堡主有何能力去界定呀<br />\n界定完又有何能力叫人跟呀<br />\n話語權只會係特區政府或者泛民手上，永遠淪唔到獨派<br />\n唔好再扮訓啦，係時候醒了"},{"pid":"2bf37f31a909bb35e9c9dccde5f4fc2ebb827e6b","tid":307014,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:54:56.000Z","msg":"熱狗五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> fatfat"},{"pid":"bc3043e8b7730d82b170cdf3d73a93d7fd106da1","tid":307014,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:56:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> fatfat</blockquote><br />\n熱狗係垃圾<br />\n唔洗再屈我水泥隊"},{"pid":"ad40734f9bbe4403d0721a2912df5e8a6c1d5d98","tid":307014,"uid":121496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"咁不如學國民黨哥套，軍政、訓政、憲政。"},{"pid":"416e5564d200c5d214b785a8093a1881ee2cffaf","tid":307014,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T13:58:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>90%人表示 本民前不嬲獨裁<br />\n<br />\n幾撚時改名做本土獨裁前線呀？</blockquote><br />\n本人100%表示你係仆街冚家剷<br />\n要落地獄 判死刑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啱唔啱語言？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n  <br />\n <img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/03/215755_50c841fb61455b4cd3533f41681a92f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F03%2F215755_50c841fb61455b4cd3533f41681a92f6.jpg&h=c5f3d6c0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}